%% render.orientation: portrait
flowchart TD
  A[Robot sends request] --> B[X-Better-Together-Robot-Token header]
  B --> C[ApplicationController authenticates BetterTogether::Robot]
  C --> D{Token digest matches enabled robot?}
  D -->|No| E[Reject as unauthenticated request]
  D -->|Yes| F[Pundit receives robot principal]
  F --> G{Requested content fits granted scope?}
  G -->|Public only| H[Allow public content]
  G -->|Community scope| I[Allow community and public content]
  G -->|Private scope| J[Allow private community and public content]
  G -->|No matching scope| K[Authorization failure]

